properties.areaDesc: Waters from Point Reyes to Pigeon Point 10-60 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 29 at 8:59AM PST until January 31 at 3:00AM PST by NWS San Francisco CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...For the first Small Craft Advisory, northwest winds 15
to 20 kt with gusts up to 25 kt and seas 9 to 11 feet at 14
seconds. For the second Small Craft Advisory, northwest winds
15 to 20 kt with gusts up to 25 kt and seas 10 to 13 feet at
19 seconds expected.

* WHERE...Waters from Point Reyes to Pigeon Point 10-60 NM.

* WHEN...For the Small Craft Advisory, until 9 PM PST this
evening. For the Small Craft Advisory, from 9 AM Thursday to 3
AM PST Friday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY NOW IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 PM PST THIS EVENING... ...SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 AM THURSDAY TO 3 AM PST FRIDAY
